import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

const FormContainer = ({ children }) => {
    return ( <
        Container >
        <
        Row className = 'justify-content-md-center' >
        <
        Col xs = { 12 }
        md = { 6 } > { children } <
        /Col> <
        /Row> <
        /Container>
    )
}

export default FormContainer
